  "text": "Skip to main content\nSign In\nSearch for Jobs\nBack to Job Posting\nSoftware Engineer\ncurrent step 1 of 7\nCreate Account/Sign In\nstep 2 of 7\nMy Information\nstep 3 of 7\nMy Experience\nstep 4 of 7\nApplication Questions\nstep 5 of 7\nVoluntary Disclosures\nstep 6 of 7\nSelf Identify\nstep 7 of 7\nReview\nCreate Account\n\nPassword Requirements:\n\nA numeric character\nA minimum of 8 characters\nA special character\nAn uppercase character\nA lowercase character\nAn alphabetic character\nEmail Address*\nPassword*\nVerify New Password*\n\nAlteryx respects your right to privacy. Our policy describes the privacy practices Alteryx employs in its collection, receipt, and use of Personally Identifiable Information (“personal information”), and explains who we are, how we collect, share and use personal information about you, and how you can exercise your privacy rights. By activating your account in Workday, you acknowledge and agree that you have read and understood Alteryx’s Privacy Policy.\n\nYou have the right to request deletion of personal information that we have collected from you. Should you wish to do so, please e-mail Alteryx’s Data Privacy Officer at privacy@alteryx.com. Written communication may also be sent to Alteryx, Inc., Attn: General Counsel, 17200 Laguna Canyon Road Irvine, CA 92618 USA.\n\nRead More\nBy checking this box, I acknowledge that I have read and agree to the terms and conditions above.\nCreate Account\nAlready have an account?\nSign In\nForgot your password?\nEnter website. This input is for robots only, do not enter if you're human.\nFollow Us\nAlteryx Privacy Policy\n© 2026 Workday, Inc. All rights reserved.",
